        "TileImage": "$($repository 0bf31415-1578-4c15-8a76-39ca2f7933d3).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to my third covert infilration challenge this one is simple and easy. If you haven&apos;t learned by now most of these challenges are meant to see how well you can get close to your target with fiber wire and kill them. Tip: Most of the Infilration methods are knocking out the right people and or using ledges or climbing or simply sliping past using finesse and AI knowledge. I also added some explosive fun with it. Have fun and happy fiber wire hunting.",
